(48, 'Stock Market Today: Dow Edges Higher; Consumer-Sentiment Steady; Gold Prices Rise — Live Updates - The Wall Street Journal', 'stock-market-today-dow-edges-higher-consumer-sentiment-steady-gold-prices-rise-live-updates-the-wall-street-journal-1760189661', 'Trump’s tariffs and the government shutdown continue to affect the economy. Follow live updates on the Dow, S&P 500, Nasdaq and other markets, including bitcoin and gold.', 'Gold climbed back above $4,000 a troy ounce, while U.S. stocks rose and oil prices tumbled as the government shutdown entered its 10th day.\r\nBettors on prediction markets increasingly anticipate the &hellip; [+1081 chars]', 'David Uberti, Matt Grossman, WSJ Staff, Spencer Jakab, Alexander Osipovich, Natalie Andrews, Heard Editors', 'articles/68ea5cdec85e6.jpg', 'published', 'The Wall Street Journal', 1, 9, '2025-10-11 10:28:16', '2025-10-11 10:34:22'),
