(53, 'Dan Orlovsky reveals what makes Eagles’ offense ‘predictable’ after ugly ‘TNF’ loss to Giants - New York Post', 'dan-orlovsky-reveals-what-makes-eagles-offense-predictable-after-ugly-tnf-loss-to-giants-new-york-post-1760189682', 'The Eagles have a bigger tell than Teddy KGB and its sinking their “predictable” offense.', 'The Eagles have a bigger tell than Teddy KGB and its sinking their &ldquo;predictable&rdquo; offense.\r\nESPN analyst and ex-NFL quarterback Dan Orlovsky slammed Philadelphia&rsquo;s offense during Thursday night&rsquo;s 34-1&hellip; [+4806 chars]', 'Matt Ehalt', 'articles/68ea5cf2c38b1.jpg', 'published', 'New York Post', 1, 14, '2025-10-11 10:30:22', '2025-10-11 10:34:42'),
